T02D1994:190a-1: shr'i badzra bhee ra ba s'a dha nam n'a ma //
T02D1994:190a-3: dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi sgrub pa'i thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D1994:190a-4: bcom ldan 'das dpal 'jigs byed ma he'i gdong pa can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1994:190a-5: bcom ldan sku mchog jig dus me ltar 'bar //
T02D1994:190a-6: rdo rje 'jigs par byed la phyag 'tshal te //
T02D1994:190a-7: de yis las rnams rab tu sgrub pa'i phyir //
T02D1994:190a-8: ma he'i gdong gi snying po'i sgrub thabs bri //
T02D1994:190a-9: yid dang mthun zhing dben pa'i gnas dag tu //
T02D1994:190a-10: dang por bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
T02D1994:190a-11: ma he'i gdong can skad cig rnal 'byor pas //
T02D1994:190a-12: lha dang bla ma mnyes byas de rjes la //
T02D1994:190a-13: stong pa ma yin mi stong ma yin pa //
T02D1994:190a-14: sems nyid spros dang bral ba rnam par bsgom //
T02D1994:190a-15: yam las rlung ste ram las bskal me 'bar //
T02D1994:190a-16: de nas h'um spros rdo rje'i rang bzhin nam //
T02D1994:190a-17: aa las zla ba rgyas pa'i steng nyid du //
T02D1994:190a-18: dh'i: las 'jam dpal gzhon nu bskyed par bya //
T02D1994:190a-19: thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rnams bsams la //
T02D1994:190a-20: de stengs h'um yig nag po 'bar ba blta //
T02D1994:190a-21: de nyid yongs su gyur pa rdo rje gdengs //
T02D1994:190a-22: thams cad yongs gyur bcom ldan ma he'i zhal //
T02D1994:190a-23: sku mdog sngo nag char sprin lta bur 'jigs //
T02D1994:190a-24: sku las me 'bar khams gsum sreg par byed //
T02D1994:190a-25: khro bo dur khrod thod pa'i do shal byas //
T02D1994:190a-26: gzhal gcig ma he nag po rgod pa'i zhal //
T02D1994:190a-27: rva gnyis par du gzhon nu'i zhal gyis brgyan //
T02D1994:190a-28: phyag g-yas rdo rje gdengs pa'i gri gug 'dzin //
T02D1994:190a-29: g-yon pa thod pa khrag gis bkang ba bsnams //
T02D1994:190a-30: zhabs gnyis gyad kyi dor stabs ro yi gdan //
T02D1994:190a-31: ma he'i nag po'i steng du rnam par bsam //
T02D1994:190b-0: mngon sum bzhin du @190b gsal bar gyur pa dang //
T02D1994:190b-1: snying gar nyi la h'um yig 'bar bar bsam //
T02D1994:190b-2: de la dgug dang bcing ba la sogs bya //
T02D1994:190b-3: de nas de nyid skar ma'i tshogs 'dras bskor //
T02D1994:190b-4: g-yeng ba med par rtag tu bzlas pa bya //
T02D1994:190b-5: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um phat /
T02D1994:190b-6: 'di ni sngags kyi rgyal po ste //
T02D1994:190b-8: 'bum phrag gsum du bzlas pa bya //
T02D1994:190b-9: de yis las rnams thams cad 'grub //
T02D1994:190b-10: gal te ldang bar 'dod pa na //
T02D1994:190b-11: ye shes ma he'i zhal la ni //
T02D1994:190b-12: mchod cing bstod pa ldang bar bya //
T02D1994:190b-13: ma he'i sbyor ba rnam par rgyu //
T02D1994:190b-14: shin tu rtogs dka'i rgyud las ni //
T02D1994:190b-15: las rnams thams cad sbyor ba'i lha //
T02D1994:190b-16: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gdams pa 'di //
T02D1994:190b-17: blo dman rnams la phan phyir bkod //
T02D1994:190b-18: dge ba cung zad thob pa des //
T02D1994:190b-19: bdag dang 'di la mos pa rnams //
T02D1994:190b-20: nad dang 'jigs sogs rab bcom nas //
T02D1994:190b-21: myur du 'jigs byed chen por shog / dpal rdo
T02D1994:190b-22: rje 'jigs byed ma he'i gdong can dpa' bo gcig
T02D1994:190b-23: pa'i sgrub thabs / slob dpon manydzu badzras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D1994:190b-25: // / bal po'i pandi ta bha ro phyag rdum dang /
